{"tid":2413850,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美制裁、5G 零件難買！華為今年智慧手機產量傳暴減逾半","createTime":"2021-02-19T04:14:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T12:10:27.000Z","uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"af09c86581018007621fb1153bbb1be9fddf7bbf","tid":2413850,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:14:34.000Z","msg":"美制裁、5G 零件難買！華為今年智慧手機產量傳暴減逾半<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2021/02/19/huawei-smartphone-production-is-rumored-to-halve-this-year/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2021%2F02%2F19%2Fhuawei-smartphone-production-is-rumored-to-halve-this-year%2F&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69GWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=2105a58c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2021/02/19/huawei-smartphone-production-is-rumored-to-halve-this-year/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國拜登政權上台後、對華為的制裁依舊，讓華為難買到 5G 零件，傳出華為已向供應商告知，今年（2021 年）華為智慧手機產量恐較 2020 年暴減逾半。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日經新聞 18 日報導，華為已向多家供應商告知生產計畫，2021 年華為智慧手機產量預估為 7,000 萬~8,000 萬支、和 2020 年相比將暴減逾半（僅不到 2020 年的一半水準），主因美國政權從川普政權轉移到拜登政權後、對華為的制裁持續，讓華為無法採購到必要的 5G 智慧手機用零件。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，美國政府自 2019 年 5 月起就階段性加強對華為的出口管制、限制供應商供應智慧手機關鍵零件給華為，而目前美國商務部雖開始允許供應商供應部分 4G 等較舊的通訊技術零件給華為，但對於 5G 關鍵零件大半未發出許可。據零件業者指出，「華為今年智慧手機產量有可能會萎縮至僅有近 5,000 萬支的水準」。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，華為年間營收規模約 14 兆日圓，其中以智慧手機為中心的消費者事業占營收比重近一半，因此智慧手機事業減速恐重擊華為的營運。據美國調查機構指出，2020 年華為智慧手機出貨量為 1.89 億支，為全球第 3 大廠，僅次於三星、蘋果，而 2021 年華為市占率恐進一步下滑。<br />\n<br />\nIDC 1 月 27 日公布調查報告指出，受蘋果 iPhone 創佳績提振，全球智慧手機市場呈現復甦、上季（2020 年 10-12 月）出貨量較去年同期成長 4.3% 至 3 億 8,590 萬支。其中，華為受美國制裁影響，出貨量暴減 42.4% 至 3,230 萬支，市占率自去年同期的 15.2%（排第 3）大幅萎縮至 8.4%、退居第 5 位。<br />\n<br />\n上季蘋果受惠 iPhone 12 系列熱賣加持，全球出貨量較去年同期大增 22.2% 至 9,010 萬支，市占率自去年同期的 19.9% 揚升至 23.4% 高居首位；三星出貨量成長 6.2% 至 7,390 萬支，市占率 19.1% 位居第 2 位；小米出貨量大增 32.0% 至 4,330 萬支，市占率 11.2% 位居第 3 位；OPPO 成長 10.7% 至 3,380 萬支，市占率 8.8% 居第 4。"},{"pid":"c8b7427269929f3e804bb0a90ef5527534b4b238","tid":2413850,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"934c985b1154572b6adc9810c56583dfac9fd656","tid":2413850,"uid":128417,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:38:43.000Z","msg":"華為居然仲有咁多貨<br />\n好想睇佢一部電話都出唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c395e563f604e4612fec570338049bdf827d2ac5","tid":2413850,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:39:31.000Z","msg":"去養豬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac07b97fe964789f814b4cab2c16df061ffe185","tid":2413850,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:39:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/eCN9glqq0VY/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FeCN9glqq0VY%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=e2b7313a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Pig-01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2FPig-01.png&h=403837ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2689564ad2d90071c9dd8505db597a59952ed654","tid":2413850,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:40:42.000Z","msg":"邊個話制裁無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced8236edc905d107620d44141b7a77adb668444","tid":2413850,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2689564ad2d90071c9dd8505db597a59952ed654","tid":2413850,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:40:42.000Z","msg":"邊個話制裁無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:42:32.000Z","msg":"拜登<br />\n